column2:
"Nice to meet you
My name is Nekonomiya♪."
"Are you going to help me? But first, you have to hear what Zect has to say, don't you?"
"I like to talk about cosmetics to use in real life on here."

"私、女の子のなりきりでやってます。
巨大化させたアクセのカジキを
かぶる時でもそうなんです。"

"女の子がカジキに丸呑みされた状態でも
体の主導権は握っているっていう
キャラ設定ですよ"
"I can't decide whether to wear a barrette or a hair slide tomorrow!"
"That screenshot I took of us and Tetra was my best yet, if I do say so myself<white><pict cute_icon><c>"
